The patch adds validity-aware search, but the vector branch filters validity after the candidate limit and the graph arm can evaluate a different default `now` than the other arms. These are correctness issues for the newly introduced search view behavior.

Full review comments:

- [P2] Apply validity before limiting vector candidates — /home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb-worktrees/orch-0.8.20-s15/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/src/lib.rs:9165-9169
